c0ac03967792f7a13","tid":411150,"uid":54995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T02:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95c18f003dfd6252ce9a8bcd710d3d423906c97","tid":411150,"uid":18725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T02:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HKFP: Pro-Beijing lawmaker Junius Ho was admitted as solicitor in England and Wales, but lacks practising certificate<br />\n<br />\n23 September 2017 08:20<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2017/09/23/pro-beijing-lawmaker-junius-ho-admitted-solicitor-england-wales-lacks-practising-certificate/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2017%2F09%2F23%2Fpro-beijing-lawmaker-junius-ho-admitted-solicitor-england-wales-lacks-practising-certificate%2F&d=CU0xZXF8PN25iZTvszaXNG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4a1f0748\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2017/09/23/pro-beijing-lawmaker-junius-ho-admitted-solicitor-england-wales-lacks-practising-certificate/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Craig Choy, the convener of the Progressive Lawyers Group, said that whether one is practising or not is crucial to the public.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;If you hold yourself out as practising, it means that you are qualified to give legal advice on the law of that jurisdiction. If a client comes to you for advice, but you are actually not practising, it is not of the best interest of the client because you may not have professional indemnity insurance covering your advice,&rdquo; he told HKFP.</span>"},{"pid":"ec684b1da097eb1cc83abe565b92857e2b1f8bbf","tid":411150,"uid":53632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢條撚樣當年點解可以做到律師會會長？全部人盲晒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n律師會既專業形象真係俾佢清曬袋<br />\n原來呢個會既會長係可以由一個有&quot;執業律師資格&quot;既人做<br />\n個會可以有幾好pro真係露曬底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b713db1218e4f5ef099e0b8c24df1afbddda69","tid":411150,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢條撚樣當年點解可以做到律師會會長？全部人盲晒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n律師會既專業形象真係俾佢清曬袋<br />\n原來呢個會既會長係可以由一個有&quot;執業律師資格&quot;既人做<br />\n個會可以有幾好pro真係露曬底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n律師會根本就係垃圾黎<br />\n<br />\n其實香港法律界, 以至法官, 都全部係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n我講個事實, 普通市民唔會明, 以為係偏激"},{"pid":"90cecd30ed3345438b99bc093bedc8961022c734","tid":411150,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢條撚樣當年點解可以做到律師會會長？全部人盲晒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n律師會既專業形象真係俾佢清曬袋<br />\n原來呢個會既會長係可以由一個有&quot;執業律師資格&quot;既人做<br />\n個會可以有幾好pro真係露曬底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n律師會根本就係垃圾黎<br />\n<br />\n其實香港法律界, 以至法官, 都全部係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n我講個事實, 普通市民唔會明, 以為係偏激</blockquote><br />\n司法獨立要建基於三權分立<br />\n香港真係人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"22ae1f7296afe0948f05bc787e50888d92e02d29","tid":411150,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"淋病撐何君堯，你地班傻仔點解唔質問淋病？<br />\n以前就識咬實689<br />\n<br />\n其實淋病咪都包庇好過份"},{"pid":"d89c41e4155825fdc20485f1ab3fab4b12054cdf","tid":411150,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.libertarianprepper.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/double_standards_3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.libertarianprepper.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F09%2Fdouble_standards_3.png&h=a73a6df0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29f5acb3edf1e03e94d9fb71c494c15738729e4f","tid":411150,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T05:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 